<i>Takumi is as old school a martial art as it gets.</i>

33:16.035 --> 33:19.622
<i>No ring, no octagon. The rules are simple.</i>

33:19.623 --> 33:21.958
<i>Known as Okinawan sumo...</i>

33:21.959 --> 33:23.334
Ohh!

33:23.335 --> 33:27.338
<i>...it looks easy. It's not.</i>

33:27.339 --> 33:30.049
<i>Your hands are wrapped in your opponent's belt.</i>

33:31.551 --> 33:34.052
<i>Object is to get him onto his back,</i>

33:34.053 --> 33:37.640
<i>both shoulders, before he does it to you.</i>

33:37.641 --> 33:39.057
Nice.

33:39.058 --> 33:41.268
<i>You land on your back for even a second,</i>

33:41.269 --> 33:43.437
<i>you lose.</i>

33:43.438 --> 33:47.441
There, he got him. Yeah. Awesome.

33:47.442 --> 33:49.944
Would you like to try? -

33:49.945 --> 33:52.780
- Try. -Yeah, sure.

33:52.781 --> 33:53.281
♪

34:09.505 --> 34:13.134
♪

34:38.117 --> 34:40.828
<i>In the end, it's a less than smoothly executed</i>

